From 35ef7b7dedc320fe721e81b32c7b43ede42e27b1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: FIM43-Redeye <14264359+FIM43-Redeye@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Feb 2026 20:42:18 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] LOCAL: debug BO fix, app health debugfs, and error ring
 buffer

Fix debug BO detach ordering: clear driver-side assignment only after
firmware confirms the detach command, preventing state mismatch on
command failure.

Improve get_app_health debugfs: iterate all connected contexts across
partitions instead of hardcoding context ID 1. Show submission/completion
counts, ctx_pc, and fatal error type per context.

Replace single-error async error cache with a 16-entry ring buffer
across aie2, aie4, and ve2. All errors are now preserved (newest-first)
and the ioctl returns as many as userspace requests. Previously only
the last error was cached and earlier errors were silently lost.
